article_title: Cars catch fire in Toms River
article_text:
Flames engulf a recreational vehicle near a Wake Forest Drive home. (Photo: Courtesy Joseph Santora)

TOMS RIVER – Toms River authorities are at a Wake Forest Drive home where multiple cars and recreational vehicles caught fire Sunday afternoon.

Few details were immediately available. Police are at the scene and the investigation is ongoing.

This is a breaking news story. Check back to app.com later for more details.

Amanda Oglesby: 732-557-5701; aoglesby@GannettNJ.com
